-- EADS/BAE Systems deal talks blocked by German government: French source
-- 
-- Wed Oct 10, 2012 10:06am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/10/10/us-eads-bae-blocked-idUSBRE8990Y220121010

 

 PARIS  (Reuters) - Merger talks between EADS and BAE Systems were blocked by the German government, a senior French government source said on Wednesday. 
 "The (German) chancellor did not want the talks to continue," the source told Reuters on condition of anonymity. (Reporting by Emmanuel Jarry; Editing by  Christian Plumb )